title: Two of our scariest stories!
description:
Two of our scariest stories.
On todays tapes...

>> Laura of the Woods
 A young boy makes a new friend in the woods… but is she who she claims to be?

>> What Was She Planning?
A man is brought home from the bar by a stranger… but the house isn’t empty.
